== Usage ==
=== Syntax ===
<pre width="75%">
{{Project heading
 | project    = <!--- Sets the project name, required --->
 | task_force = <!--- Sets the task force name, if a task force --->
 | border     = <!--- Sets the border color on the box --->
 | bgcolor    = <!--- Sets the background color on the box --->
 | image      = <!--- Sets the image, required --->
 | size       = <!--- Changes the default image size from 275px --->
}}
</pre>

=== Example ===

==== Colors ====
;Hex -
<pre width="33%">
{{Project heading
 | project = Beer
 | image   = Kranz Koelsch.jpg
 | border  = #CC9000
 | bgcolor = #F3DE94
}}
</pre>

Will yield this:
{{Project heading |project=Beer |image=Kranz Koelsch.jpg |border=#CC9000 |bgcolor=#F3DE94}}

;Color -
<pre width="33%">
{{Project heading
 | project = Beer
 | image   = Kranz Koelsch.jpg
 | border  = red
 | bgcolor = pink
}}
</pre>

Will yield this:
{{Project heading |project=Beer |image=Kranz Koelsch.jpg |border=red |bgcolor=pink}}

==== General usage ====
<pre width="33%">
{{Project heading
 | project    = Beer
 | task_force = Pubs
 | image      = MeophamGreen3573.JPG
}}
</pre>

Will yield this:
{{Project heading |project=Beer |task_force=Pubs |image=MeophamGreen3573.JPG}}

